------------------------
TangoCMS NEWS (Basic ChangeLog for Users)
------------------------

A complete ChangeLog can be found at http://tangocms.org/changelog


2.6.0 (2010-11-13)
========================

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* Feature #65: Run Zula via CLI, with upgrade ability
	* Feature #67: Finish Internationalisation/Localisation support.
	* Feature #83: More consistent media module
	* Feature #130: Additional Contact Details
	* Feature #187: Bulk import / upload of items to Media
	* Feature #204: Toggle displaying of Article published information in Headlines and Categories
	* Feature #247: Assign different edit permissions to different pages
	* Feature #265: Article Auto Expire Time/Date
	* Feature #271: Different theme styles
	* Feature #278: Read more option for page breaks
	* Feature #279: RSS feeds should obey page breaks
	* Feature #284: Media image watermarks
	* Feature #290: Display media videos in widescreen 16:9 format
	* Feature #302: Add PHP lint check in build.sh utility
	* Feature #308: Add a usable left sidebar to 'carbon' theme
	* Feature #309: Display email address in contact form email body
	* Feature #314: Line numbers in the CSS textarea
	* Feature #316: Improve the poll duration options
	* Feature #318: Change default login type to 'email'
	* Feature #319: Reset password, ask for email instead of username

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #238: Don't generate physical captcha files
	* Bug #276: Permissions reset when changing the order of items in content layout
	* Bug #283: 202 error with uploaded mp3 file in media player
	* Bug #303: Article headlines links to wrong URL when displaying from all categories
	* Bug #305: Unable to select suggestion with the arrow keys from aliases auto-completion
	* Bug #306: Settings shows cache type as 'Disabled' instead of 'File' after install
	* Bug #310: Ordering pages requires permission associated with the menu module
	* Bug #315: No check for TLS/SSL support before offering as email encryption
	* Bug #322: Email encryption 'TLS' does not support 'STARTTLS'
	* Bug #323: TinyMCE theme toolbar double the height in MSIE8


2.5.5 (2010-06-15)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #275: Page anchors don't function as expected
	* Bug #293: Arbitrary limit for poll options not obeyed
	* Bug #295: JS autocomplete doesn't work without SEF URLs
	* Bug #301: WYSIWYG editor page break causes random HTML 'p' elements
	* Bug #304: SQL password that contains double quote results in internal error


2.5.4 (2010-05-18)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	*  Bug #285: Zula 'Locale' lib conflicts with PHP intl extension


2.5.3 (2010-04-06)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #260: SQL query error in Media module


2.5.2 (2010-04-03)
========================

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* Feature #253: Display a close button (Tangobox)

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #252: AJAX/Inline data closes on button click (Tangobox)
	* Bug #249: zula_human_readable() is given an object in Media_controller_add
	* Bug #250: file inputs look ugly in MSIE, and border on hover in chrome
	* Bug #255: Media, no error message about invalid mime type
	* Bug #256: Password reset redirects to non existent page
	* Bug #259: SQL query error upon registering new users


2.5.1 (2010-03-21)
========================

-- Security Fixes

	* Security #237: File Upload Filter Bypass in TangoCMS <=2.5.0

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* Feature #234: Upgrade to TinyMCE 3.3 final

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #208: Timezone is not always correctly set, and incorrect dates shown
	* Bug #233: Session password expire, can still view various URLs
	* Bug #240: Email signature prepends 2 new lines
	* Bug #241: WYSIWYG editor does not load with 'standard' router type
	* Bug #242: Themes file inputs have a border around them
	* Bug #243: Media thumbnails have a black background in the image


2.5.0 (2010-02-17)
========================

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* Feature #198: Expire users passwords
	* Feature #200: Lock user accounts so they can not login
	* Feature #209: Display image title/description
	* Feature #212: Slideshow for images
	* Feature #218: Add a 'description' field to Content Layout when managing attached modules
	* Feature #221: Microsoft Web App Gallery installer
	* Feature #225: Move 'Mange Validations' from Users to Session module
	* Feature #227: Upgrade to jQuery 1.4

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #205: Manually adding editor shebang with TinyMCE does not change editor type
	* Bug #210: Contact form converts input options to lowercase
	* Bug #214: Media upload not work under Windows
	* Bug #217: Don't install Media module if PHP 'gd' extension is not available
	* Bug #219: Page Quick Edit Moves Pages in Page Hierarchy
	* Bug #222: overlayOpacity does not work in MSIE
	* Bug #223: Duplicate menu in content layout breaks W3C validation
	* Bug #230: Unable to change case of a group name


2.4.0 (2009-12-14)
========================

-- Security Fixes

	* Security #188: Media item physical files can be viewed outside of TCM, bypasses ACL checks

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* Feature #145: True 'remember me' feature
	* Feature #149: Different anti-spam methods
	* Feature #150: Custom module wrap class names via Content Layout
	* Feature #152: Allow redirectable URL Aliases
	* Feature #164: Show user id/username in contact email
	* Feature #165: Menu items 'title' attribute text
	* Feature #178: Search/Filter in modules configuration
	* Feature #182: Clone/Copy Layout in Content Layout
	* Feature #186: Add support for Google's CDN
	* Feature #191: Lightbox support for Media module

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #167: Editor URLs are incorrect with 'standard' router
	* Bug #176: Incorrect query string delimiter with 'standard' router in many places
	* Bug #177: Innocent theme: 'white-space: nowrap' makes media item titles unreadable
	* Bug #179: Ugmanager lib issue with duplicate usernames that are digit
	* Bug #183: Page at frontpage, tags are not displayed
	* Bug #184: Tags keep loosing first value when editing a page
	* Bug #185: Unable to remove any tags from a page
	* Bug #189: Poll only allows 1 vote from guests (IPv6 IP addresses only)
	* Bug #190: CST != CET
	* Bug #193: Validator_Is lib will not work with IPv6 addresses
	* Bug #201: PHP bug causes pre-installation checks false positive on Windows



2.3.3 (2009-09-03)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #170: Invalid translation id in aliases module
	* Bug #172: RSS fatal error when 'Number of items per feed' set to 0
	* Bug #173: Incorrect pagination URL at frontpage with 'standard' router
	* Bug #174: Issue with table prefix over 12 chars long when installing


2.3.2 (2009-08-04)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #168: Installation will fail if 'tmp' is not writable to start with


2.3.1 (2009-07-26)
========================

-- Bug Fixes

	* Bug #154: Installer doesn't check if './tmp' subdirectories are writable
    * Bug #155: Installer Cappuccino theme needs polish/fixes
    * Bug #156: Menu item URL '/' does not link to frontpage
    * Bug #157: Article part picker URL, query string is encoded
    * Bug #158: Display/Force title does not effect frontpage/requested module
    * Bug #159: Pagination URL is incorrect at URL '/admin'
    * Bug #160: WYSIWYG Editor styles need improving
    * Bug #162: Only modules in SC should use pagination page arg
    * Bug #163: '+' char is allowed in URL, causes 404 error
    * Bug #166: Possible login redirection loop


2.3.0 (2009-06-29)
========================

-- Security Fixes

	* #149 "XSS issue in Html lib (and so Contact module)"

-- Feature Improvements/Modifications

	* #42 "Content Tagging"
	* #54 "Different layout on pages"
	* #62 "Simple WYSIWYG content editor"
	* #64 "Rewrite comments to be a module"
	* #66 "Submission to news sites"
	* #67 "Finish Internationalisation/Localisation support."
	* #73 "Reduce HTTP requests for CSS and JS files"
	* #86 "Restricted logins after failed attempts"
	* #95 "SSL Support with Login"
	* #109 "Configurable Login Destination"
	* #129 "TLS/SSL option in Email settings"
	* #134 "Session Register Terms and Conditions"

-- Bug Fixes

	* #51 "Permission issues when admin inherits from root"
	* #82 "Users module doesn't check if username exists upon edit/add"
	* #91 "Windows only Issue: view file does not exist (when it actually does) for poll module"
	* #96 "Installer gives wrong URL at last stage for 'AdminCP' when using 'standard' router"
	* #100 "Simple Profile instead of 403 Permission error show if logged in and no permission"
	* #104 "The install doesn't work on a Windows Server 2003 box with IIS 6.0"
	* #111 "No pages and articles with umlauts"
	* #118 "Internal error when no media category is selected for deletion"
	* #132 "Problem Installing on WAMPserver 2.0 with Windows Vista"
	* #138 "Cappucino theme - H1 is white"
